{"tid":2196212,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"MOS Burger 預告2個月內連開3店","createTime":"2020-09-09T17:04:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T06:57:03.000Z","uid":225931,"like":52,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"7e6e5538ba913d64298cd11dd5705587a4992ede","tid":2196212,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T17:04:03.000Z","msg":"MOS Burger已進駐香港14年，由9月15日起，全線分店將會推出秋日限定的吉列帆立貝漢堡。MOS Burger亦預告9月、10月將分別進駐黃埔、大埔及長沙灣，以全新面貌登場。<br />\n<br />\n日本品牌在香港似乎特別吃香，MOS Burger亦宣佈再度疫市擴張。3間新分店將會陸續在9月2日、9月中旬 及10月上旬分別登陸黃埔、大埔及長沙灣。大埔新店更是區內第二間分店；而長沙灣分店選址麗閣商場，場內設有多個「打卡」位。於MOS Burger享用漢堡包後，更可到各個塗鴉貨櫃前拍照留念。<br />\n<br />\n顧客凡於上述三間新分店消費滿 150元，即可獲贈MOS購物袋。同時，因應MOS Burger進駐香港14周年，品牌亦推出限定的「吉列帆立貝漢堡」；於全線MOS Burger分店有售。吉列帆立貝餅以原粒帆立貝入饌，再配以風味十足的橙皮檸檬醬汁及海鮮醬。"},{"pid":"dd50283357c39fa8b9ef11362909990151657c4d","tid":2196212,"uid":204539,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T17:05:34.000Z","msg":"香港分店係咪直屬日資先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed897ec87c67c778d23425074c95464d8ec1d48","tid":2196212,"uid":225931,"like":3,"dislike":98,"score":-95,"quote":{"pid":"dd50283357c39fa8b9ef11362909990151657c4d","tid":2196212,"uid":204539,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T17:05:34.000Z","msg":"香港分店係咪直屬日資先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T17:07:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da211e832f86c172f79233f38920eb18fdc8fd4","tid":2196212,"uid":204539,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2ed897ec87c67c778d23425074c95464d8ec1d48","tid":2196212,"uid":225931,"like":3,"dislike":98,"score":-95,"quote":{"pid":"dd50283357c39fa8b9ef11362909990151657c4d","tid":2196212,"uid":204539,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T17:05:34.000Z","msg":"香港分店係咪直屬日資先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"